you maye doe so: for I call the Gods to witnesses that the wordes
which I speake, and the loue I protest to Mamillia is verytie
without vanity, trueth without trifling: fayth without flattery, as
fine within, as fayre without; a siluer sheath with a golden dagger,
and in token she shal haue both lands and life, hand and heart, as
her own for euer.
            
